wikipedia_page.main: Sir Peter Malden Studd  (15 September 1916 – 22 June 2003) was an English cricketer and the 643rd Lord Mayor of London.

response: His great-nephew Sir Peter Malden Studd was also Lord Mayor of London, from 1970 to 1972.
*Peter Malden Studd (1916–2003) – cricketer and Lord Mayor of London.
*Sir Peter Malden Studd (1916–2003), Lord Mayor of London (1970–1971)
